{"title_page": "Shafaq Naaz", "text_new": "{{Use Indian English|date=December 2013}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2013}}\n{{Indian name|Shafaq|Naaz}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Shafaq Naaz\n| image              = Shafaq Naaz in 2019.jpg\n| caption            = Naaz in 2019\n| birth_date         = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1993|02|07}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/birthday-celebration-shikha-ankita-shafaq-and-azad-150207|title=Birthday celebration for Shikha, Ankita, Shafaq and Azad|date=2015-02-07|website= Tellychakkar Dot Com|access-date=2020-02-02}}</ref>\n| birth_place        = [[Meerut]], [[Uttar Pradesh]], India\n| residence          = [[Mumbai]], [[Maharashtra]], [[India]]\n| occupation         = [[India|indian ]], model\n| years_active       = 2010 - present\n| nationality        = {{IND}}n\n| spouse             = \n| relatives          = Sister- Falaq Naaz\n| website            = {{url|www.shafaqnaaz.com}}\n}}\n'''Shafaq Naaz''' (born 7 February 1993)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/birthday-celebration-shikha-ankita-shafaq-and-azad-150207|title=Birthday celebration for Shikha, Ankita, Shafaq and Azad|date=2015-02-07|website= Tellychakkar Dot Com|access-date=2020-02-02}}</ref>  is an [[India]]n [[television]] [[actress]]. She is known for portraying [[Kunti]] in ''[[Mahabharat (2013 TV series)|Mahabharat]]'' and Mayuri in ''[[Chidiya Ghar]]''. She was also seen as Vrinda in ''[[Mahakali- Anth hi Aarambh hai]]''. Recently she played a pivot role as lead in a web series called ''Halala'' for ULLU app ( March 2019), which showcased the issues stemming post Triple Talaq in the Muslim community.\n\nShafaq is also a trained Kathak dancer.\n\n== Television ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-  style=\"background:#b0c4de; text-align:center;\"\n! Year !! Serial !! Role !! Channel !! Description\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Sapna Babul Ka...Bidaai]]'' || Guni || [[Star Plus]] || Episode 644 onwards\n|-\n| 2