app ( March 2019), which showcased the issues stemming post Triple Talaq in the Muslim community.\n\nShafaq is also a trained Kathak dancer.\n\n== Television ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-  style=\"background:#b0c4de; text-align:center;\"\n! Year !! Serial !! Role !! Channel !! Description\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Sapna Babul Ka...Bidaai]]'' || Guni || [[Star Plus]] || Episode 644 onwards\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Sanskaar Laxmi]]'' || Randhal || [[Zee TV]] ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2011 || rowspan=\"2\" | ''[[Crime Patrol (TV series)|Crime Patrol]]'' || Riya || rowspan=\"2\" | [[Sony Entertainment Television (India)|SET India]] || Episode 42 (17 September 2011)\n|-\n| Trupti ||  Episode 57 (11 November 2011)\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[Shubh Vivah]]'' || Karuna Saxena || [[Sony Entertainment Television (India)|SET India]] || Episodes 1-89 (27 February - 29 June 2012)\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[Fear Files]]'' || Neha Paranjape || [[Zee TV]] || Episode 3 (7 July 2012)\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[Teri Meri Love Stories]]'' || Pari || [[Star Plus]] || Episode 5 (25 August 2012)\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[Love Marriage Ya Arranged Marriage]]'' || Pooja || [[Sony Entertainment Television (India)|SET India]] ||\t\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[Gumrah: End of Innocence|Gumrah (Season 2)]]'' || Pallavi || [[Channel V India|Channel V]] || Episode 86 (15 October 2012 )\n|-\n| 2013 || ''[[Madventures (ARY Digital show)|Madventures]]'' || Herself (Contestant) || [[ARY Digital]] || Episodes 1-4 (22 February - 15 March 2013)\n|-\n| 2013 || ''[[Savdhaan India]]'' || Harpreet Sandhu (Victim) || [[Life OK]] || Episode 257 (25 April 2013)\n|-\n| 2013&ndash;2014 || ''[[Mahabharat (2013 TV series)|Mahabharat]]'' || [[Kunti]] || [[Star Plus]] || Episode 16-267\n|-\n| 2014\u20132017 || ''[[Chidiya Ghar]]'' || Mayuri Gomukh Narayan || [[SAB TV]] || Episode 755 (13 October 2014) onwards\n|-\n|2018 ||'' [[Mahakali- Anth hi Aarambh hai]]'' || Vrinda || [[Colors TV]] || Episode 59-95\n|-\n|2018 ||''[[Kulfi Kumar Bajewala]]'' || Niyati, a junior doc